Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 07 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Ulnar tunnel syndrome' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Distal flattening of the ulnar nerve, proximal swelling' checkbox is enabled
And 'Increased T2w signal of the ulnar nerve' checkbox is enabled
And 'Protrusion of the transverse carpal ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Peritendinous fluid flexor carpi ulnaris tendon' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thickening tendon sheath flexor carpi ulnaris muscle' checkbox is enabled

And 'Chronic idiopatic' radio button is enabled
And 'Secondary' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Secondary' radio button
Then 'Osseous origin' radio button is enabled
And 'Synovial origin' radio button is enabled
And 'Neurogene/vascular origin' radio button is enabled
And 'Soft tissue mass' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Osseous origin' radio button
Then 'Os triquetrum' checkbox is enabled
And 'Os pisiforme' checkbox is enabled
And 'Os hamatum' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'Dislocation' radio button is enabled
And 'Degeneration' radio button is enabled
And 'Tumor' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Fracture' radio button
Then 'Hypertrophic callus formation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pseudarthrosis Hamulus ossis hamati' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Degeneration' radio button
Then 'Hypertrophic osteophytes' checkbox is enabled


When I select 'Synovial origin' radio button
Then 'Ganglion cyst' radio button is enabled
And 'Tenosynovitis' radio button is enabled
And 'Tenosynovial giant cell tumor' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Ganglion cyst' radio button
Then 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
When I enter any value from 1 to 80 in 'Max. diameter' input field
Then '2nd plane' input field is enabled
When I enter any value from 1 to 80 in '2nd plane' input field
Then '3rd plane' input field is enabled


When I select 'Neurogene/vascular origin' radio button
Then 'Soft tissue tumor' radio button is enabled
And 'Aneurysm of the ulnar artery' radio button is enabled
And 'Thrombosis of the ulnar artery' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Aneurysm of the ulnar artery' radio button
Then 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Length' input field is enabled



When I select 'Soft tissue mass' radio button
Then 'Calcification' radio button is enabled
And 'Soft tissue tumor' radio button is enabled
And 'Lipomatosis' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Postoperative' radio button
Then 'Incompletely split retinaculum' radio button is enabled
And 'Nerve injury in the surgical field' radio button is enabled
And 'Perineural fibrosis of the carpal tunnel' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Nerve injury in the surgical field' radio button
Then 'Complete cut' checkbox is enabled
